domain name: host name + domain name + type: such as: www.linuxcast.net;

DNS: domain name system;

mapping domain name and IP: www.linuxcast.net   <--->    61.1.1.1

resolve domain name: gethostbyname();

resolving by the following way: fiel(/etc/hosts, /etc/networks), DNS, NIS;

control the enquiry order by configuring: /etc/nsswitch.conf: "hosts: file dns"

command for enquiry DNS: "host, dig": dig www.linuxcast.net

